result.title: 2006 The Marine Conservation Society - Seasearch, Various locations in Dorset, Diver observations and detailed survey records
result.name: 2006-the-marine-conservation-society-seasearch-various-locations-in-dorset-diver-observations-a
result.notes:
Data from Seasearch dives undertaken in Dorset in 2006. All survey records from individual dives, Seasearch weekends and specific studies are all included. In many cases, records are compiled from more than one form where divers were in close proximity to each other and covered the same habitats.
     Photographs taken on Dorset Wildlife Trust charter weekends are held by DWT in Dorchester. 
     Records are verified post survey and biotopes are assigned according the information available by DWT using the MNCR 04.05 key.
